title: Bug 109350 - Output parameter not displaying in data set dialog
OB: While on the query result page, no data is returned and the output parameter is not displayed in the edit data set dialog.
EB: The output parameter should be displayed in the data set dialog along with other details. Specifically, it should be shown in the edit data set dialog.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Call the stored procedure from the Oracle database. 2. Check the query result page for no data returned. 3. Observe that the output parameter is not displayed in the edit data set dialog.
